<div class="teacher-header"><h1>Mette Bengtsson-Pratt</h1><div class="sm"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/Mymettayoga-240185076501719/" title="Facebook"><svg class="icon icon-facebook2"><use xlink:href="#icon-facebook2"></use></svg><span>Facebook</span></a></div></div><p>I started to practice Yoga in my late 20's. After years of curiosity I finally dared to go to a class. I loved it and it became a regular practice straight away. I had lower back problems, bad posture and other minor health issues. It didn't take very long to realise an improvement in my physical health and I also started experiencing other benefits.</p>